<LegalLayout title="Security">
  <h1>Security at ZansAI</h1>
  <p>Security is our top priority. We are committed to protecting your data and maintaining your trust.</p>

  <h2>Infrastructure Security</h2>
  <p>Our platform runs on a globally distributed edge network with built-in DDoS protection and automatic failover. All data is encrypted in transit using TLS 1.3 and at rest using AES-256 encryption.</p>

  <h2>Compliance</h2>
  <p>ZansAI is SOC 2 Type II compliant and GDPR ready. We regularly undergo third-party security audits and penetration testing to ensure our systems remain secure.</p>

  <h2>Access Control</h2>
  <p>We employ strict access controls and principle of least privilege for our internal systems. Multi-factor authentication (MFA) is enforced for all employee access to critical infrastructure.</p>

  <h2>Vulnerability Disclosure</h2>
  <p>We welcome reports from the security research community. If you believe you have found a vulnerability in one of our products or services, please let us know by emailing security@zansai.com.</p>
</LegalLayout>
